  "text": "To deal with PPM complexities, such as uncertainty or dependencies among projects, it is essential to keep track of data and ensure that critical data is not eliminated or unnecessary data incorporated. This process has to be traceable (backwards and forwards throughout the decision cycle and from the strategic to operational levels) [CITATION_1] .",
